          <div class="post-toc">

            
              
            

            
              <div class="post-toc-content"><ol class="nav"><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#u4E00_u3001_u91CF_u5316_u6295_u8D44_u4ECB_u7ECD"><span class="nav-number">1.</span> <span class="nav-text">一、量化投资介绍</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u6709_u6548_u5E02_u573A_u5047_u8BF4"><span class="nav-number">1.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">有效市场假说</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u4E3B_u52A8_u6295_u8D44_u7684_u4E0D_u8DB3"><span class="nav-number">1.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">主动投资的不足</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u7406_u67E5_u5FB7_B7_u585E_u52D2_uFF08Richard_Thaler_uFF09_u7406_u8BBA"><span class="nav-number">1.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">理查德·塞勒（Richard Thaler）理论</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u884C_u4E3A_u7ECF_u6D4E_u5B66"><span class="nav-number">1.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">行为经济学</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u4E3B_u89C2_u6295_u8D44_u4E0E_u91CF_u5316_u6295_u8D44_u7684_u533A_u522B"><span class="nav-number">1.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">主观投资与量化投资的区别</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u6536_u76CA_u7387_28return_29__u516C_u5F0F"><span class="nav-number">1.6.</span> <span class="nav-text">收益率(return) 公式</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#Alpha__u7684_u975E_u5E38_u89C4_u5B9A_u4E49_uFF1A"><span class="nav-number">1.6.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">Alpha 的非常规定义：</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u5BBD_u5BA2_28Quant_29"><span class="nav-number">1.7.</span> <span class="nav-text">宽客(Quant)</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u4E00_u4E2A_u5B8C_u6574_u7684_u91CF_u5316_u4EA4_u6613_u7CFB_u7EDF"><span class="nav-number">1.8.</span> <span class="nav-text">一个完整的量化交易系统</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#u4E8C_u3001_u91CF_u5316_u5FC5_u5907_u80A1_u7968_u57FA_u7840_u77E5_u8BC6"><span class="nav-number">2.</span> <span class="nav-text">二、量化必备股票基础知识</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u4EA4_u6613_u51B3_u7B56_u8FC7_u7A0B"><span class="nav-number">2.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">交易决策过程</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u5206_u65F6_u56FE_u4E0EK_u7EBF_u56FE_u7684_u6570_u636E_u5904_u7406"><span class="nav-number">2.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">分时图与K线图的数据处理</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u6280_u672F_u6307_u6807"><span class="nav-number">2.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">技术指标</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#MA-_u79FB_u52A8_u5747_u7EBF_28Moving_Average_29"><span class="nav-number">2.3.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">MA-移动均线(Moving Average)</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#KD-_u968F_u673A_u6307_u6570"><span class="nav-number">2.3.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">KD-随机指数</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#RSI-_u76F8_u5BF9_u5F3A_u5F31_u6307_u6570"><span class="nav-number">2.3.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">RSI-相对强弱指数</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u6280_u672F_u6307_u6807_u7684_u5E94_u7528_u6280_u5DE7"><span class="nav-number">2.3.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">技术指标的应用技巧</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u6280_u672F_u6307_u6807_u7684_u5E94_u7528_u539F_u5219"><span class="nav-number">2.3.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">技术指标的应用原则</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u66F4_u591A_u7684_u4EA4_u6613_u51B3_u7B56_u4F9D_u636E"><span class="nav-number">2.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">更多的交易决策依据</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u96C6_u5408_u7ADE_u4EF7"><span class="nav-number">2.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">集合竞价</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u64AE_u5408_u4EA4_u6613_u539F_u7406"><span class="nav-number">2.5.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">撮合交易原理</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u96C6_u5408_u7ADE_u4EF7_u65F6_u95F4_u7EBF"><span class="nav-number">2.5.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">集合竞价时间线</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u9664_u6743_u3001_u590D_u6743"><span class="nav-number">2.6.</span> <span class="nav-text">除权、复权</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u9664_u6743/_u9664_u606F_u539F_u56E0"><span class="nav-number">2.6.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">除权/除息原因</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u590D_u6743_u539F_u56E0"><span class="nav-number">2.6.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">复权原因</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u590D_u6743_u65B9_u5F0F"><span class="nav-number">2.6.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">复权方式</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u6253_u65B0_u3001_u914D_u80A1"><span class="nav-number">2.7.</span> <span class="nav-text">打新、配股</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u6253_u65B0_u80A1"><span class="nav-number">2.7.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">打新股</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u914D_u80A1"><span class="nav-number">2.7.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">配股</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u516C_u544A_u7814_u62A5_u793E_u4EA4_u5A92_u4F53"><span class="nav-number">2.8.</span> <span class="nav-text">公告研报社交媒体</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u5904_u7406_u975E_u7ED3_u6784_u5316_u6570_u636E_u7684_u76F8_u5173_u6280_u672F_uFF1A"><span class="nav-number">2.8.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">处理非结构化数据的相关技术：</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u8D8B_u52BF_u5206_u6790_u548C_u91CF_u4EF7_u5206_u6790"><span class="nav-number">2.9.</span> <span class="nav-text">趋势分析和量价分析</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u8D8B_u52BF_u5206_u6790"><span class="nav-number">2.9.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">趋势分析</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u5BF9_u652F_u6491_u548C_u538B_u529B_u7684_u7406_u89E3_uFF1A"><span class="nav-number">2.9.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">对支撑和压力的理解：</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u91CF_u4EF7_u65F6_u7A7A"><span class="nav-number">2.9.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">量价时空</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#u91CF_u4EF7_u5206_u6790_u7684_u6838_u5FC3_u95EE_u9898"><span class="nav-number">2.9.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">量价分析的核心问题</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#u53C2_u8003_u4E66_u7C4D"><span class="nav-number">2.10.</span> <span class="nav-text">参考书籍</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></div>
            

